# =====================================
# iMak Trading Japan - Monorepo .gitignore
# Created: 2026-04-25
# =====================================

# === SECRETS (must never be committed) ===
**/API key.txt
**/api_key.txt
**/ebay keys.txt
**/gemini_key.txt
**/groq_key.txt
**/openai_key.txt
**/anthropic_key.txt
**/credentials.json
**/service_account*.json
double-hold-*.json
*.pem
*.key

# === Python ===
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.tox/

# === Virtual env ===
.venv/
venv/
env/

# === IDE ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# === OS ===
desktop.ini
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
ehthumbs.db

# === Excel/Office temp ===
~$*.xlsx
~$*.xls
~$*.docx

# === Logs ===
*.log
psa_run_*.log
**/logs/

# === Cache files (regeneratable) ===
**/*_cache.json
**/cache/
**/data/*_cache.json
**/bandai_*_cache.json
**/pokemon_*_cache.json
**/psa_cache.json

# === Generated CSV outputs (regeneratable) ===
**/csv_output/*.csv
**/csv_output/*.json
**/ebay_upload_*.csv
**/tcg_upload_*.csv
**/tshirt_upload_*.csv
**/gshock_upload_*.csv
**/porter_upload_*.csv
**/ichibankuji_upload_*.csv

# === Review/audit logs (regeneratable) ===
**/review_logs/*.jsonl
**/review_logs/*.md
**/audit_logs/*.md

# === Sold data (large, regeneratable) ===
**/sold_data/*.xlsx
**/sold_data/*.csv

# === Misc temp/test outputs ===
**/_*.csv
**/scout_result.xlsx
**/tmp/
**/temp/
*.tmp

# Worktree marker (各 worktree のローカルファイル、git track しない)
.PROJECT_LOCKED.md
